  "last_post_content": "\ud83d\udcdd Lessons we learned the hard way.\nPlatform architects surface lessons from production.\n\nTopic: 60 SQL Interview Questions From Beginner to Advanced (2026)\n\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Infrastructure as code prevents configuration drift.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Progressive rollouts save sleep. 1% \u2192 10% \u2192 100%.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Automation beats heroics. Every manual step is a future incident.\n\nThe pattern: enhances system reliability and team productivity.\n\nWhat's a lesson that changed how you work?\n\n#DBT #SAPHANA #SSIS #Automation #Python #SSRS #Databricks\n\n\u2753 What would you add to this list?\n\n#SSIS #Automation #MySQL #Python #Insights #BigQuery #Oracle",
